**  ER (ERROR-MESSAGE)
E-1 INPUT RECEIVING FACTORY FOR PRINTING
E-2 INPUT THE RECEIVING PLACE FOR PRINTING
E-3 RECEIVING IS EACH FACTORY OF AOYAMA
E-4 RECEIVING PLACE DOESN'T MATCH CONDITION OF RCV FACTORY
E-5 FIXED SETTING NUMBER IS NOT INPUT
E-6 ACCOMODATED QUANTITY IS NOT INPUT
E-7 ACCOMODATED QUANTITY UNIT IS NOT INPUT
E-8 SETTING CODE IS NOT INPUT
E-9 TURN SETTING CODE INTO NUMBER
E-10 THERE IS NOT SETTING CODE IN SETTING M/F
E-11 BARREL A IS NOT INPUT
E-12 BARREL B IS NOT INPUT
E-13 BARREL B IS BIGGER THAN BARREL A
E-14 BARREL A MUST BE A MULTIPLE OR SAME AS BARREL B
E-15 L.T IS NOT INPUT
E-16 COEFFICIENT IS NOT INPUT
E-17 THERE IS NOT IT IN KANBAN KIND M/F
E-18 PAPER IS NOT INPUT
E-19 PAPER CODE IS DIFFERENT FROM PAPER CODE OF THE LOWER
E-20 COMPLETION UNIT WEIGHT IS NOT INPUT
E-21 DRAWING NECESSARY INSTRUCTION IS (BLANK,1,4)
E-22 INPUT SORT INSTRUCTION OF LOCATION FUNCTION M/F
E-23 THERE IS NOT REVERSING CONDITION CODE IN M/F
E-24 ALL BLANK AT PROCESSING CONDITION IS NOT FORGIVEN
E-25 THERE IS NOT PLATING SECTION IN BAR CODE M/F
E-26 PLATING TYPE IS NOT INPUT
E-27 THERE IS NOT PLATING TYPE IN SECTION LT M/F
E-28 THERE IS NOT PRESENT PROCESS SECTION IN BAR CODE M/F
E-29 PRESENT PROCESS TYPE IS NOT INPUT
E-30 THERE IS NOT PRESENT PROCESS TYPE IN SECTION LT M/F
E-31 THERE IS NOT PRECEDING PROCESS SECTION IN BAR CODE M/F
E-32 PRECEDING PROCESS SECTION TYPE IS NOT INPUT
E-33 THERE ISN'T PRECEDING PROCESS SECT TYPE IN SECT LT M/F
E-34 KANBAN NUMBER OF SHEETS HAVE TO BE LESS THAN 3 COLUMNS
E-35 BECAUSE KANBAN IS MADE ON OLD DAYS REMAKE THEM ALL
E-36 BECAUSE KANBAN CONTENTS BECAME A CHG, CHG EFF DATE
E-37 LOCATION IS WRONG
E-38 INPUT PROVISION POINT
E-39 THERE IS NOT APPLICABLE DATA IN PART NAME M/F
